#. (itstool) path: component/name
#: org.kde.gcompris.appdata.xml:16
msgid "GCompris"
msgstr "GCompris"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.gcompris.appdata.xml:17
msgid "Educational game for children"
msgstr "Haurrentzako joko hezigarria"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.gcompris.appdata.xml:19
msgid ""
"GCompris is a high quality educational software suite, including a large "
"number of activities for children aged 2 to 10."
msgstr ""
"GCompris kalitate handiko hezkuntza-software multzo bat da, 2 eta 10 urte "
"bitarteko haurrentzako jarduera ugari dituena."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.gcompris.appdata.xml:20
msgid ""
"Some of the activities are game orientated, but nonetheless still "
"educational."
msgstr ""
"Jardueretako batzuk jolasera zuzenduak daude, hala eta guztiz ere, heztea "
"dute helburu."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.gcompris.appdata.xml:22
msgid ""
"Below you can find a list of categories with some of the activities "
"available in that category."
msgstr ""
"Behean kategoria zerrenda bat aurki dezakezu, kategoria horretan erabilgarri "
"dauden jardueretako batzuekin batera."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.gcompris.appdata.xml:25
msgid "computer discovery: keyboard, mouse, different mouse gestures, etc."
msgstr ""
"ordenagailua ezagutzea: teklatua, sagua, saguaren keinu ezberdinak, etab."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.gcompris.appdata.xml:26
msgid ""
"arithmetic: table memory, enumeration, mirror image, balance the scale, "
"change giving, etc."
msgstr ""
"aritmetika: taulak oroitzea, zenbaketa, irudi ispilatua, balantza orekatu, "
"diru xehea itzultzea, etab."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.gcompris.appdata.xml:28
msgid "science: the canal lock, color mixing, gravity concept, etc."
msgstr ""
"zientzia: ubidearen uhatea, koloreak nahastea, grabitate kontzeptua, etab."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.gcompris.appdata.xml:29
msgid "games: memory, connect 4, tic tac toe, sudoku, hanoi tower, etc."
msgstr ""
"jokoak: oroimena, 4 konektatu, artzain-jokoa, sudoku, hanoi dorrea, etab."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.gcompris.appdata.xml:30
msgid "reading: reading practice, etc."
msgstr "irakurketa: irakurtzen trebatzea, etab."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.gcompris.appdata.xml:31
msgid ""
"other: learn to tell time, the braille system, maze, music instruments, etc."
msgstr ""
"bestelakoak: ikasi ordua esaten, braille sistema, labirintoa, musika-"
"tresnak, etab."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.gcompris.appdata.xml:34
msgid ""
"Currently GCompris offers in excess of 100 activities and more are being "
"developed. GCompris is free software, that means that you can adapt it to "
"your own needs, improve it and, most importantly, share it with children "
"everywhere."
msgstr ""
"Gaur egun GCompris-ek 100 jardueratik gora eskaintzen ditu eta gehiago "
"garatzen ari dira. GCompris software askea da, horrek esan nahi du zure "
"beharretara egokitu dezakezula, hobetu dezakezula eta, garrantzitsuagoa "
"dena, haurrekin partekatu dezakezu dauden lekuan daudela."

